---
import heroImage from '../assets/revenue_matters_hero.png';
---

<section class="service-detail-section">
	<div class="service-detail-container">
		<!-- Hero Image -->
		<div class="service-hero">
			<img 
				src={heroImage.src} 
				alt="Revenue &amp; Administrative Matters Lawyer in Noida" 
			/>
		</div>

		<!-- Main Content and Sidebar -->
		<div class="service-content-wrapper">
			<!-- Main Content -->
			<div class="service-main-content">
				<h1>Revenue &amp; Administrative Matters Lawyer in Noida</h1>
				
				<p class="intro-text">
					Resolving disputes concerning agricultural land, land revenue records, and administrative actions requires a thorough command of local land revenue codes and administrative procedures. Our specialized revenue court advocates in Noida provide authoritative legal representation before Tehsil, SDM, DM, and Commissioner courts to secure your land boundaries, update mutations, and resolve government notice disputes.
				</p>

				<h2>What We Handle</h2>
				<ul class="service-features">
					<li>
						<strong>Administrative Court Representation:</strong> Strategic advocacy in trials, hearings, and disputes before Tehsil, SDM, DM, and Divisional Commissioner Courts
					</li>
					<li>
						<strong>Land Mutation (Dakhil-Kharij):</strong> End-to-end legal assistance for resolving contested, delayed, or fraudulent mutation entries in municipal and land records
					</li>
					<li>
						<strong>Demarcation &amp; Boundary Disputes:</strong> Filing suits for official government land survey demarcation (Meeras) and resolving encroachment conflicts
					</li>
					<li>
						<strong>Revenue Appeals &amp; Revisions:</strong> Drafting and prosecuting formal appeals against adverse land orders before higher revenue boards and commissioners
					</li>
					<li>
						<strong>Khasra &amp; Khatauni Corrections:</strong> Correcting administrative registry errors, wrong ownership shares, and illegal entries in land records
					</li>
					<li>
						<strong>Government &amp; Authority Notice Replies:</strong> Drafting precise, legally sound replies to notices served by Noida, Greater Noida, or Yamuna Expressway authorities
					</li>
				</ul>

				<h2>Why Choose Our Firm</h2>
				<p>
					Revenue court matters are highly specialized and governed by complex state-specific statutes like the UP Revenue Code, 2006. Our firm excels by offering:
				</p>
				<ul class="benefits-list">
					<li>Deep legal command over land laws, local revenue procedures, and state land records</li>
					<li>18+ years of extensive litigation practice in local Tehsil, SDM, and DM courts</li>
					<li>Expertise in analyzing complex historical land maps, partition records, and revenue sheets</li>
					<li>Located in Noida , Greater Noida , Jewar , Khurja , Sikardarabad , Bulandshehar with convenient access to District Collectorate and Administrative offices</li>
					<li>Results-driven, transparent counsel with a proven track record of securing clean land possessions</li>
				</ul>

				<h2>Our Approach</h2>
				<p>
					We protect your agricultural and residential land holdings through meticulous record audits and aggressive litigation. We:
				</p>
				<ol class="approach-list">
					<li>Perform a rigorous check of Khasra, Khatauni, registry deeds, and historical mutations</li>
					<li>Verify title histories and inspect local revenue department survey records</li>
					<li>Draft and file structured plaints, written statements, or replies before the appropriate magistrate</li>
					<li>Manage coordinate actions during official on-site land demarcations and surveys</li>
					<li>Argue client interests persuasively before the revenue collector, commissioner, or SDM</li>
					<li>Enforce revenue decrees to update official government portals and restore land ownership</li>
				</ol>

				<h2>Protect Your Land &amp; Property Records</h2>
				<p>
					If you are struggling with a boundary encroachment, incorrect land records, or facing legal actions from local land authorities in Noida, Greater Noida, Khurja, Sikanderabad, Bulandshehar, we can help you in:
				</p>
				<ul class="complaint-list">
					<li>Filing partition suits for joint holdings and agricultural land division</li>
					<li>Responding to public land encroachment notices and contesting eviction orders</li>
					<li>Liaisoning with revenue officers (Lekhpal / Kanungo) for error corrections</li>
					<li>Contesting illegal land acquisitions and seeking fair statutory compensations</li>
					<li>Representation and litigation support before Revenue & Administrative Authorities including Tehsildar, SDM, DM, and Commissioner Courts</li>
					<li>Providing certified copies, legal drafting, filing, arguments, and order-related assistance for revenue matters. </li>
				</ul>

				<div class="cta-section">
					<p>Need expert revenue court counsel or facing an agricultural land boundary dispute? Contact us to schedule a consultation.</p>
					<a href="/contact" class="cta-button">Get Legal Help</a>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Sidebar Services Links -->
			<aside class="service-sidebar">
				<div class="sidebar-box">
					<h3>Our Services</h3>
					<nav class="services-nav">
						<a href="/court-marriage" class="service-link">
							Court Marriage Registration
						</a>
						<a href="/cyber-lawyers" class="service-link">
							Cyber Crime Lawyer
						</a>
						<a href="/criminal-lawyers" class="service-link">
							Criminal Lawyer
						</a>
						<a href="/corporate-lawyers" class="service-link">
							Corporate & Industrial Disputes
						</a>
						<a href="/consumer-lawyers" class="service-link">
							Consumer Protection Lawyer
						</a>
						<a href="/civil-lawyers" class="service-link">
							Civil Lawyer
						</a>
						<a href="/revenue-matters" class="service-link active">
							Revenue & Administrative Matters
						</a>
						<a href="/property-registration" class="service-link">
							Property Registration
						</a>
						<a href="/notary-lawyer" class="service-link">
							Notary Lawyer
						</a>
					</nav>
				</div>
			</aside>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.service-detail-section {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff 0%, #f0f4f8 100%);
		padding: 2rem 1rem 4rem;
		min-height: 100vh;
	}

	.service-detail-container {
		max-width: 1200px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	/* Hero Image */
	.service-hero {
		width: 100%;
		height: 400px;
		border-radius: 12px;
		overflow: hidden;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
		box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.12);
	}

	.service-hero img {
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		object-fit: cover;
	}

	/* Content Wrapper */
	.service-content-wrapper {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 320px;
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	/* Main Content */
	.service-main-content h1 {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		font-weight: 900;
		color: #0f172a;
		margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
		line-height: 1.2;
	}

	.service-main-content h2 {
		font-size: 1.6rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		color: #0f172a;
		margin: 2.5rem 0 1rem 0;
		line-height: 1.3;
	}

	.intro-text {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		color: #475569;
		line-height: 1.8;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.service-main-content p {
		color: #475569;
		line-height: 1.7;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		font-size: 1rem;
	}

	.service-features,
	.benefits-list,
	.complaint-list {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
	}

	.service-features li,
	.benefits-list li,
	.complaint-list li {
		padding: 0.75rem 0 0.75rem 2rem;
		position: relative;
		color: #475569;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	.service-features li::before,
	.benefits-list li::before,
	.complaint-list li::before {
		content: "→";
		position: absolute;
		left: 0;
		color: #0ea5a4;
		font-weight: bold;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
	}

	.service-features li strong {
		color: #0f172a;
	}

	.approach-list {
		padding-left: 2rem;
		color: #475569;
		line-height: 1.7;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.approach-list li {
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
		color: #475569;
	}

	.approach-list li::marker {
		color: #0ea5a4;
		font-weight: bold;
	}

	/* CTA Section */
	.cta-section {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0fffe 0%, #e0f7f6 100%);
		padding: 2rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
		margin-top: 2.5rem;
		border-left: 4px solid #0ea5a4;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.cta-section p {
		font-size: 1.05rem;
		color: #0f172a;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		font-weight: 500;
	}

	.cta-button {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 0.875rem 2rem;
		background: #0ea5a4;
		color: white;
		text-decoration: none;
		border-radius: 8px;
		font-weight: 700;
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(14, 165, 164, 0.2);
	}

	.cta-button:hover {
		background: #0d8e8d;
		transform: translateY(-2px);
		box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(14, 165, 164, 0.3);
	}

	/* Sidebar */
	.service-sidebar {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 1.5rem;
	}

	.sidebar-box {
		background: white;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
		position: sticky;
		top: 100px;
		height: fit-content;
	}

	.sidebar-box h3 {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		color: #0f172a;
		margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
		padding-bottom: 1rem;
		border-bottom: 2px solid #e2e8f0;
	}

	/* Services Navigation */
	.services-nav {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 0.5rem;
	}

	.service-link {
		display: block;
		padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
		color: #475569;
		text-decoration: none;
		border-radius: 6px;
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
		border-left: 3px solid transparent;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
	}

	.service-link:hover {
		background: #f0fffe;
		color: #0ea5a4;
		border-left-color: #0ea5a4;
		transform: translateX(4px);
	}

	.service-link.active {
		background: #f0fffe;
		color: #0ea5a4;
		border-left-color: #0ea5a4;
		font-weight: 600;
	}

	/* Responsive Design */
	@media (max-width: 1024px) {
		.service-content-wrapper {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr 280px;
		}

		.service-main-content h1 {
			font-size: 2rem;
		}

		.service-hero {
			height: 300px;
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.service-detail-section {
			padding: 1.5rem 1rem 3rem;
		}

		.service-content-wrapper {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 1.5rem;
		}

		.sidebar-box {
			position: static;
		}

		.service-main-content h1 {
			font-size: 1.6rem;
		}

		.service-main-content h2 {
			font-size: 1.3rem;
		}

		.service-hero {
			height: 250px;
			margin-bottom: 2rem;
		}

		.services-nav {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
			gap: 0.5rem;
		}

		.service-link {
			font-size: 0.9rem;
			padding: 0.6rem 0.75rem;
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 480px) {
		.service-detail-section {
			padding: 1rem;
		}

		.service-main-content h1 {
			font-size: 1.3rem;
		}

		.service-main-content h2 {
			font-size: 1.1rem;
			margin-top: 1.75rem;
		}

		.service-hero {
			height: 200px;
			margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		}

		.intro-text {
			font-size: 1rem;
		}

		.cta-section {
			padding: 1.5rem 1rem;
		}

		.services-nav {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.sidebar-box {
			padding: 1rem;
		}
	}
</style>
